# Calculator

Just a basic RESTful API with Symfony 5.4

## Installation

Use the github.com/rafaelucena/asr_calculator, download the project, then:

```bash
# gets the project installed
$ composer install

# gets the project running
$ php -S 127.0.0.1:8000 -t public/
```

## Usage

There are 4 routes enabled for the requests, methods configured are GET and POST only:

127.0.0.1:8000/api/addition/{valueA}/{valueB}
127.0.0.1:8000/api/subtraction/{valueA}/{valueB}
127.0.0.1:8000/api/multiplication/{valueA}/{valueB}
127.0.0.1:8000/api/division/{valueA}/{valueB}

## Tests
```bash
# Run the unit tests configured
$ bin/phpunit tests
```

